rComments: He is an awesome professor, always makes himself available for student questions. Although he is moody and the course content is challenging, he advises students on how to study and tries his best to help those who are willing to study.

Although there is a lot of  content in this class, he was enthusiastic about the topic and eager to answer any questions. He provided sample questions for the test and reminded students to keep up with the lecture material. Overall, he is a very good lecturer and instructor :)
Long lectures..very filled slides..lots of memorizing event the slightest details...not aways clear...he was clear in his lectures but way too much stuff to memorize!
